snippet.title: Eclectic Guests Trailer
snippet.description:
Eclectic Guests is an experimental narrative puzzle game about exploring a surreal hotel made from hand crafted paper cutouts. Game by Julia Del Matto.

Song: Tattooed Man by Coil
